(Zuixian Restaurant)

26
00:02:03,630 --> 00:02:05,400
Today, you invited me over

27
00:02:05,940 --> 00:02:07,490
not just for a simple welcome party,

28
00:02:08,390 --> 00:02:09,400
right?

29
00:02:11,140 --> 00:02:12,610
Nanfeng, don't worry.

30
00:02:13,350 --> 00:02:14,370
Today,

31
00:02:14,740 --> 00:02:16,330
we're just here to catch up.

32
00:02:17,790 --> 00:02:18,730
By the way,

33
00:02:19,350 --> 00:02:21,330
I almost forgot to congratulate you.

34
00:02:22,070 --> 00:02:23,670
The Jing Clan has once again won

35
00:02:23,670 --> 00:02:25,240
the championship of the Tea Contest.

36
00:02:25,700 --> 00:02:27,170
Congratulations.

37
00:02:28,460 --> 00:02:29,400
You flatter me.

38
00:02:29,950 --> 00:02:32,400
I have no merit in this matter.

39
00:02:32,550 --> 00:02:35,170
Instead, we've taken the spotlight

40
00:02:36,230 --> 00:02:37,170
away from you.

41
00:02:37,390 --> 00:02:39,890
Here, I apologize to you.

42
00:02:40,350 --> 00:02:41,290
Put it down.

43
00:02:42,460 --> 00:02:44,650
Nanfeng, you're wrong.

44
00:02:44,950 --> 00:02:45,950
How can you say

45
00:02:45,950 --> 00:02:46,830
you have no merit

46
00:02:46,830 --> 00:02:48,330
in this?

47
00:02:48,700 --> 00:02:50,620
If it weren't for your revival,

48
00:02:50,620 --> 00:02:52,210
turning around the Jing Clan's fortune,

49
00:02:52,620 --> 00:02:54,280
how could Luo Zhusi, a mere woman,

50
00:02:54,860 --> 00:02:56,960
have accomplished such a great feat?

51
00:02:57,300 --> 00:02:58,770
We can't put it that way.

52
00:03:00,350 --> 00:03:01,520
Now that you're back,

53
00:03:02,620 --> 00:03:03,800
we should definitely

54
00:03:04,070 --> 00:03:05,560
keep in touch.

55
00:03:14,580 --> 00:03:17,280
If you just want

56
00:03:18,140 --> 00:03:19,110
to have tea

57
00:03:19,110 --> 00:03:20,050
or drink with me,

58
00:03:20,230 --> 00:03:22,370
I'm always available.

59
00:03:23,180 --> 00:03:24,070
But if you want

60
00:03:24,070 --> 00:03:25,520
to get close to the Chief

61
00:03:25,990 --> 00:03:27,090
of Jinyu Tea,

62
00:03:27,580 --> 00:03:29,100
you might be barking up the wrong tree.

63
00:03:29,620 --> 00:03:30,720
The current Chief

64
00:03:31,070 --> 00:03:32,490
is my sister-in-law.

65
00:03:35,230 --> 00:03:36,560
So what?

66
00:03:37,460 --> 00:03:39,840
Isn't it just a matter of time?

67
00:03:41,270 --> 00:03:42,370
However I see it,

68
00:03:42,990 --> 00:03:44,960
Jinyu Tea should rightfully be yours.

69
00:03:45,390 --> 00:03:46,850
Everyone thinks so.

70
00:03:48,390 --> 00:03:49,450
Luo Zhusi

71
00:03:49,670 --> 00:03:53,700
is just a usurper.

72
00:03:53,700 --> 00:03:55,210
We can't say it like that.

73
00:03:55,580 --> 00:03:57,300
The tribute tea she made

74
00:03:57,300 --> 00:03:58,720
is there for all to see.

75
00:03:58,900 --> 00:04:01,330
I don't want people to gossip

76
00:04:01,510 --> 00:04:04,140
that I took over a plum job

77
00:04:04,140 --> 00:04:05,800
from a woman's hands,

78
00:04:05,990 --> 00:04:08,000
reaping the benefits without effort.

79
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,490
Even if I were to sit on it,

80
00:04:12,950 --> 00:04:15,170
I wouldn't sit securely, right?

81
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:21,180
No wonder we're brothers.

82
00:04:22,140 --> 00:04:23,140
With one heart,

83
00:04:23,700 --> 00:04:24,660
I've already

84
00:04:25,100 --> 00:04:26,860
thought this through for you.

