Two liang of Anzhou Sweetie.

98
00:04:57,140 --> 00:04:58,140
Line up for shopping.

99
00:04:58,140 --> 00:04:59,200
Come back when you finish.

100
00:05:00,020 --> 00:05:01,060
Ma'am, may I ask

101
00:05:01,420 --> 00:05:02,580
how long I have to wait?

102
00:05:02,580 --> 00:05:03,620
Let me see your number.

103
00:05:04,380 --> 00:05:05,420
No. 240.

104
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:07,340
You'd better wait outside.

105
00:05:07,340 --> 00:05:08,300
We're too busy here.

106
00:05:08,540 --> 00:05:10,060
I don't want Anzhou Sweetie.

107
00:05:10,260 --> 00:05:11,220
Do you have Aji Tea?

108
00:05:11,460 --> 00:05:12,380
Give me some Aji Tea.

109
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:13,640
We don't have Aji Tea here.

110
00:05:13,780 --> 00:05:14,700
Only Anzhou Sweetie.

111
00:05:14,820 --> 00:05:16,060
Anzhou Sweetie is the best.

112
00:05:16,700 --> 00:05:17,720
If you want Aji Tea,

113
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:19,580
you have to go
to the main store of Jinyu Tea.

114
00:05:20,020 --> 00:05:21,500
Well, then.

115
00:05:22,620 --> 00:05:23,460
No. 199.

116
00:05:23,460 --> 00:05:24,700
Two liang of Anzhou Sweetie.

117
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:25,660
Mine, mine.

118
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:27,540
So many people.

119
00:05:28,060 --> 00:05:28,900
What would you like?

120
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:29,920
- Come.
- Anzhou Sweetie.

121
00:05:29,940 --> 00:05:30,900
Alright.

122
00:05:30,900 --> 00:05:35,380
(New: Anzhou Sweetie, limited
to two liang per person per day)

123
00:05:36,660 --> 00:05:37,800
Is there any Anzhou Sweetie?

124
00:05:38,020 --> 00:05:39,280
Sorry, it's sold out for today.

125
00:05:39,580 --> 00:05:40,460
Alright.

126
00:05:40,460 --> 00:05:41,380
Come back in two days.

127
00:05:41,380 --> 00:05:42,340
Alright.

128
00:05:44,100 --> 00:05:47,700
(New: Anzhou Sweetie, limited
to two liang per person per day)

129
00:05:47,700 --> 00:05:48,820
I'm exhausted.

130
00:05:58,100 --> 00:05:59,020
Jing Kan,

131
00:05:59,700 --> 00:06:00,700
have you heard?

132
00:06:00,700 --> 00:06:01,860
Everyone is saying

133
00:06:01,860 --> 00:06:04,180
that Luo Aji is
Luo Zhusi's illegitimate child.

134
00:06:06,660 --> 00:06:07,780
You know what?

135
00:06:07,780 --> 00:06:08,740
It's actually possible.

136
00:06:10,260 --> 00:06:11,300
They also say

137
00:06:11,540 --> 00:06:12,620
that Grandfather's death

138
00:06:12,620 --> 00:06:14,340
might have something to do
with Luo Zhusi.

139
00:06:15,780 --> 00:06:16,980
I'm not sure about that.

140
00:06:17,540 --> 00:06:18,740
I also heard

141
00:06:19,220 --> 00:06:20,900
that Luo Zhusi pushed Grandmother

142
00:06:20,900 --> 00:06:22,260
so she fell.

143
00:06:23,060 --> 00:06:24,300
Don't talk nonsense.

144
00:06:24,780 --> 00:06:25,960
She wasn't even home that day.

145
00:06:26,780 --> 00:06:27,620
Come on.

146
00:06:27,620 --> 00:06:29,060
I'm just chatting with you.

147
00:06:31,660 --> 00:06:32,740
I just feel

148
00:06:32,980 --> 00:06:35,380
that it's Uncle who spread these rumors.

149
00:06:36,260 --> 00:06:37,220
Uncle?

150
00:06:38,220 --> 00:06:39,220
Why?

151
00:06:39,220 --> 00:06:40,140
Think about it.

152
00:06:40,380 --> 00:06:41,320
Before Uncle came back,

153
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:42,840
there weren't so many rumors about us.

154
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:43,860
Ever since he came back,

155
00:06:43,860 --> 00:06:45,240
all kinds of rumors have come out.

156
00:06:45,620 --> 00:06:46,580
And one day,

157
00:06:46,980 --> 00:06:48,940
I saw Uncle go to Luo Zhusi's room.

158
00:06:49,300 --> 00:06:50,860
He came out after a while,

159
00:06:51,060 --> 00:06:52,820
and I saw Luo Zhusi looking haggard.

160
00:06:54,020 --> 00:06:56,040
Don't you think
she's a bit intimidated by Uncle?

161
00:06:56,660 --> 00:06:57,380
Moreover,

162
00:06:57,380 --> 00:06:58,430
after she won the contest,

163
00:06:58,430 --> 00:06:59,840
she's been in low spirits all day.

164
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:00,760
It's just not normal.

165
00:07:01,420 --> 00:07:03,180
Why are you caring about her now?

166
00:07:04,140 --> 00:07:05,300
It's not really caring.

167
00:07:05,740 --> 00:07:06,940
When I put myself in her shoes,

168
00:07:06,940 --> 00:07:08,480
I think she's also having a tough time.

169
00:07:09,060 --> 00:07:10,020
Alright.

170
00:07:10,460 --> 00:07:11,800
Let's not talk about her anymore.

171
00:07:13,260 --> 00:07:14,720
You must be tired after a whole day.

172
00:07:15,020 --> 00:07:16,180
What do you want for dinner?

173
00:07:16,420 --> 00:07:17,420
What about a full set?

174
00:07:17,420 --> 00:07:18,290
Forget it.

175
00:07:18,290 --> 00:07:19,500
I can't always have that.

176
00:07:19,620 --> 00:07:21,180
I can't stand it.

177
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:24,180
I heard the roasted pork trotters

178
00:07:24,180 --> 00:07:25,780
in South Market

179
00:07:25,780 --> 00:07:27,060
are really delicious.

180
00:07:30,140 --> 00:07:31,860
Alright, I want that.

181
00:07:32,910 --> 00:07:33,760
- Let's go.
- Yeah.

182
00:07:33,780 --> 00:07:34,920
How about we split it?

183
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:36,180
- I can't finish it.
- No way.

184
00:07:36,180 --> 00:07:37,140
No.

185
00:07:39,300 --> 00:07:40,220
Everyone's here.

186
00:07:41,540 --> 00:07:43,700
Mr. An, shall we get started?

187
00:07:46,460 --> 00:07:48,860
Recently,
we've had two pieces of good news.

188
00:07:50,220 --> 00:07:52,500
One is that Jinyu Tea

189
00:07:52,660 --> 00:07:55,260
won the championship of the Tea Contest.

190
00:07:56,660 --> 00:07:57,580
The other is

191
00:07:58,540 --> 00:08:00,980
that my son Nanfeng has returned safely.

192
00:08:02,700 --> 00:08:03,820
According to the old rule,

193
00:08:04,570 --> 00:08:05,940
the Chief of Jinyu Tea

194
00:08:06,660 --> 00:08:08,540
should be continued

195
00:08:08,540 --> 00:08:09,820
by the contest winner.

196
00:08:10,620 --> 00:08:11,580
However, recently,

197
00:08:12,140 --> 00:08:13,820
relatives and local gentry

198
00:08:14,140 --> 00:08:16,540
have been coming to discuss this issue.

199
00:08:17,140 --> 00:08:19,140
I think we should

200
00:08:19,140 --> 00:08:20,940
all sit down and talk

201
00:08:23,300 --> 00:08:24,940
to avoid any future conflicts

202
00:08:24,940 --> 00:08:26,540
in Jinyu Tea.

203
00:08:28,780 --> 00:08:31,060
I think Wei Junyi's actions

204
00:08:31,220 --> 00:08:32,740
have always been fair.

205
00:08:34,980 --> 00:08:37,100
Speaking of which,
Jinyu Tea's success today

206
00:08:38,260 --> 00:08:40,260
also owes a lot
to the help of all the relatives.

207
00:08:41,060 --> 00:08:42,860
It's good to discuss.

208
00:08:43,900 --> 00:08:46,620
I think we should decide by voting.

209
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:49,820
One vote for me,

210
00:08:50,420 --> 00:08:51,460
one vote for Mr. An,

211
00:08:52,060 --> 00:08:53,380
one vote for Cousin,

212
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:55,020
one vote for the first branch,

213
00:08:55,060 --> 00:08:56,480
and one vote for the second branch.

214
00:08:56,540 --> 00:08:58,580
As for me, I'll state my position first.

215
00:08:59,260 --> 00:09:01,220
I support Luo Zhusi

216
00:09:01,420 --> 00:09:03,580
to continue as the Chief of Jinyu Tea.

217
00:09:06,140 --> 00:09:07,740
I agree with Wei Junyi

218
00:09:08,460 --> 00:09:10,140
and highly recognize

219
00:09:10,140 --> 00:09:12,080
Chief Luo's previous contributions
to Jinyu Tea.

220
00:09:12,220 --> 00:09:14,500
Moreover, Wei Junyi's willingness

221
00:09:14,900 --> 00:09:16,900
to vote for someone
from outside the family

222
00:09:17,140 --> 00:09:18,300
shows her broad-mindedness

223
00:09:18,300 --> 00:09:20,020
and magnanimity.

224
00:09:20,500 --> 00:09:22,100
That's not quite right, Cousin.

225
00:09:24,060 --> 00:09:26,500
Chief Luo is from outside the family,

226
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:28,740
but she is my daughter-in-law.

227
00:09:29,220 --> 00:09:30,380
She married my son.

228
00:09:32,300 --> 00:09:33,500
Nanfeng is my son.

229
00:09:34,060 --> 00:09:37,380
Both are my flesh and blood.

230
00:09:40,700 --> 00:09:42,100
That may be so,

231
00:09:42,460 --> 00:09:45,220
but the principle is not like that.

232
00:09:45,940 --> 00:09:46,860
Jing Nanfeng

233
00:09:46,980 --> 00:09:48,860
is Dayou's only son now.

234
00:09:49,500 --> 00:09:50,740
He's also the eldest son.

235
00:09:51,020 --> 00:09:53,220
We thought he had perished,

236
00:09:53,580 --> 00:09:54,580
so Jinyu Tea had

237
00:09:54,580 --> 00:09:55,860
to be temporarily managed

238
00:09:56,100 --> 00:09:57,620
by Chief Luo.

239
00:09:58,020 --> 00:09:59,380
But now that he's back,

240
00:09:59,660 --> 00:10:00,620
Chief Luo

241
00:10:00,980 --> 00:10:02,340
is no longer legitimately suitable

242
00:10:02,460 --> 00:10:03,300
to be the Chief

243
00:10:03,300 --> 00:10:04,900
of Jinyu Tea.

244
00:10:05,420 --> 00:10:07,020
As the saying goes,

245
00:10:07,460 --> 00:10:09,660
no legitimacy, no authority.

246
00:10:09,860 --> 00:10:12,500
No authority, no success.

247
00:10:12,820 --> 00:10:15,500
Fairness lies in people's hearts.

248
00:10:16,100 --> 00:10:17,060
That makes sense.

249
00:10:17,540 --> 00:10:19,620
The business surely goes to the son.

250
00:10:20,380 --> 00:10:21,540
They're having a discussion.

251
00:10:21,540 --> 00:10:22,860
Don't make a fuss.

252
00:10:24,740 --> 00:10:25,700
I

253
00:10:26,020 --> 00:10:27,500
vote for Jing Kan.

254
00:10:28,700 --> 00:10:31,340
Though Jing Kan didn't win
the Tea Contest,

255
00:10:31,740 --> 00:10:33,220
the Anzhou Sweetie he made

256
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:34,780
is clearly getting better,

257
00:10:35,180 --> 00:10:37,500
showing a trend of establishing the new.

258
00:10:38,500 --> 00:10:40,100
The future of Jinyu Tea is with him.

259
00:10:40,460 --> 00:10:41,980
He is the future of Jinyu Tea.

260
00:10:42,500 --> 00:10:43,460
Moreover,

261
00:10:45,220 --> 00:10:46,580
he also has the surname Jing.

262
00:10:47,180 --> 00:10:48,200
If you don't vote for him,

263
00:10:48,580 --> 00:10:49,740
who else can you vote for?

264
00:10:50,980 --> 00:10:51,940
Mr. An,

265
00:10:52,660 --> 00:10:55,500
Jing Kan is not within the scope

266
00:10:55,500 --> 00:10:57,140
of our discussion today.

267
00:10:59,580 --> 00:11:01,100
So, we can only choose

268
00:11:01,860 --> 00:11:03,460
between Jing Nanfeng

269
00:11:03,460 --> 00:11:04,420
and Luo Zhusi?

270
00:11:04,540 --> 00:11:05,460
That's right.

271
00:11:06,980 --> 00:11:08,140
I abstain.

272
00:11:16,740 --> 00:11:17,780
Let me say something.

273
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:23,380
I vote for Chief Luo.

274
00:11:25,980 --> 00:11:27,260
Today, we are here

275
00:11:27,660 --> 00:11:28,740
to choose a chief,

276
00:11:29,580 --> 00:11:30,580
not to discuss

277
00:11:31,100 --> 00:11:32,780
who Jinyu Tea belongs to.

278
00:11:33,780 --> 00:11:35,460
Jinyu Tea is the lifelong effort

279
00:11:36,020 --> 00:11:37,100
of my parents.

280
00:11:37,500 --> 00:11:38,460
I believe

281
00:11:38,460 --> 00:11:40,780
Chief Luo is more capable

282
00:11:41,100 --> 00:11:42,340
of managing Jinyu Tea than I am.

283
00:11:43,340 --> 00:11:44,460
Thank you all

284
00:11:44,740 --> 00:11:45,780
